title: Refrigerator FASTENER HANDLE ASM
description: Refrigerator FASTENER HANDLE ASM ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 9 Reviews PartSelect Number PS16619453 Manufacturer Part Number WR01X39781 This part is the replacement door handle fastener for your refrigerator. It is made of white plastic and metal, is sold individually, and measures approximately 1-1/4 inches by 1 inch. The door handle fastener allows you to connect your door handle to the refrigerator door. If your door handle is loose or missing, this is the part that will replace it. This part is an authentic OEM part sourced directly from the manufacturer.

installationInstructions.author: David from BENICIA, CA
installationInstructions.title: lower pull out drawer handle fastener to freezer was broken on one side.
installationInstructions.content: I ordered the plastic fastener, that held the handle to the freezer door.after I received the part I used a screw driver to attach the fastener to the door.  Then I placed the handle onto the fastener and bumped the handle with my hand to the left. this attached the handle to the door.
